    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some visible clear coat peeling on the hood and a few minor door dings consistent with its mileage. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid, but the suspension is starting to feel loose and will likely need attention in the coming year. The interior is intact but shows wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It\u2019s a functional car for someone looking for basic transportation without the high price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
